{"type": "article", "id": 52299, "title": "HAY 与音响品牌 SONOS 合作，配色耳目一新｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-18T23:34:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 49466, "name": "Hay"}, {"id": 5706, "name": "Sonos"}, {"id": 49467, "name": "BD Barcelona Design"}, {"id": 49468, "name": "Amron Experimental"}, {"id": 31050, "name": "Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte"}, {"id": 49469, "name": "Matteo Tosi"}, {"id": 49470, "name": "Kodai Iwamoto"}, {"id": 29372, "name": "Stephen Burks"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180418194902q5Tko4UZgyhVtAW3.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #a8a9ae; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #a8a9ae} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #a8a9ae; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #a8a9ae} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #a8a9ae; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #a8a9ae} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Stircle by Amron Experimental</h3><p>纽约产品设计工作室 Amron Experimental 推出了一种搅拌饮品的创新方式。这种解决方案名叫 Stircle。她能够在不使用任何搅拌棒的情况下混合所有成分，使用者只要将饮品杯放置在 Stircle 内，便可直接等待饮品自动搅拌完成。</p><p>工作室创始人 Scott Amron 谈到做这款产品的初衷时表示，“每天都有 4 亿根搅拌棒被扔进垃圾桶，这让我十分困扰，木质搅拌棒破坏坏境，塑料材质搅拌棒也是一样。我们需要减少垃圾，减少二氧化碳排放量，降低成本，种植更多树木。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=e0632bygvsd&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418194944v9geU2y6SxWNzcFr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418194944VipA3jSUCPuRFtGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418194944mc8FkMJYLjbzPKrv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418194943gxmKjC4aiU8lwLdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.581250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.amronexperimental.com/Stircle.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Amron Experimental</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Grasso by Stephen Burks for BD Barcelona Design</h3><p>西班牙家具品牌 BD Barcelona Design 推出 Grasso 皮革座椅系列，操刀这个系列的是设计工作室 Stephen Burks Man Made 的创始人 Stephen Burks 。</p><p>Grasso 系列包括休闲椅，脚凳和吧台组成，试验将不同材料用于室内装饰的不同部位。Burks 与 Bolon 一起设计了一系列新型纺织品，用于 Grasso 系列中的装饰元素。新的材料用于皮革休闲椅的背面和侧面，以及脚凳的底部。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0632j2t72m&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195027QASlEUbV9JvGhsHC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195028RfpEXacLshdg7Yik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804181950319QzCG2nWAMO05m4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.965313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195031mLrEHbMUcYT0NvKB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.718697\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/04/18/stephen-burks-furniture-collection-bd-barcelona-design-bolon-textiles/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Limited-edition Collection by Hay&amp;Sonos</h3><p>丹麦家居设计品牌 HAY 与音响品牌 SONOS 合作，创造出一系列限量版音响，他们称这次的作品“值得像家具一样被对待”。</p><p>这次限量版产品的原型是 Sonos Play1 扬声器，HAY 赋予了其符合品牌审美的配色，旨在适应不同的家庭环境。</p><p>Hay for Sonos 限量版系列也适用苹果的 AirPlay 系统，这意味着它可以无线连接家中的电视机、智能手机和其他音频设备，将于今年 9 月推出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195138s8g2Fzb4Vp1yajIh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804181951429rlqmVzxHLb1uUwG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195143jUEaQB2HiPhF0Aq1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195145nxQIUiz3kT68KCp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195145yVRZ14nLh0bYr8GI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Plastic Blowing project by Kodai Iwamoto</h3><p>日本设计师 Kodai Iwamoto 使用玻璃吹制技术将塑料管材改造成花瓶，最近在米兰设计周展出。Plastic Blowing 项目，希望将大量生产的材料转变成艺术品。</p><p>他将玻璃吹制的老式制造工艺与通常用于管道中的便宜易得的 PVC 管结合起来。首先，设计师在加热器上加热 PVC 管 15 至 20 分钟，直到其表面呈现出柔软的粘稠橡胶状态。然后，他将管道放入一个木制模具中，并通过类似于玻璃吹制的方式创作花瓶。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195214UV8jSxD4tF92RKXB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195214eJq1L9W3YRrGf42H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195215Y6Vn0pemW9G8Lk3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195216nKGxtAaDqgRZ1kTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195217FSj8QWBhX7mnU9oA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.181049\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nontiscordardimé and Adelina by Matteo Tosi</h3><p>设计师 Matteo Tosi 在米兰家具展上推出了两个新系列 Nontiscordardimé 和 Adelina。</p><p>Nontiscordardimé 是一组五颜六色的桌子，桌面由一系列横平竖直的线条和几何形状组成，另有花瓶、收纳盘等附件，也可以单独使用。Adelina 是一系列饰有几何形状和线条的装饰品，饰有对比鲜明的黑色和金色饰面，可用于放置物品。这个系列以 Matteo Tosi 的祖母的名字命名，让人想起与家人和朋友一起用餐的记忆。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195244sWHDnQASIVvkR8at.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195244qB5GMuN8SaUVKXe9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195244YWoN0HkLrZC76POb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195245feAOQIWxcrBYVMH2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195245pwlfP2ZBYry4O9go.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195244L3X5F4v6SeY8PUnI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://matteodesign.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">matteodesign.it</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Isola: A Leather Coffee Table by Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte</h3><p>比利时设计师 Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte 在布鲁塞尔开设了一家自己的设计工作室。他在米兰家具展上推出一款名为 Isola 的咖啡桌。在粉末涂层的钢制框架外，包裹着黑色、天然色系的皮革，给人一种紧绷绷的感觉。</p><p>这种经久耐用的皮革材料往往被用于奢侈品设计。但这种桌面的紧绷感可能会随着时间变松变软，当发生这种情况时，可以使用手柄将其拉紧，就像它是全新的一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195341J17Qc4K5bBDp2Pi0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804181953414UgeowRpuTiSkz7E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195341ZPsgxikeQhj5RMN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195341w3mUAJN85TnuLDs6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195341g0mhKVo3qMYbD97v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418195342MlNeiJksvhAnZCVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.841406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.pierreemmanuelvandeputte.com/work/2018/isola.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}